	  (gst_service_installed) and (gst_service_list_any_installed).
	  (gst_service_bsd_set_status): added
	* time-conf.in: made it to use gst_service_list_any_installed ()
	* replace.pl.in: (gst_replace_slackware_hostname),
	  (gst_replace_rcinet1conf), (gst_replace_rcinet1conf_global),
	  (gst_replace_wireless_opts): functions added to replace in slackware
	  network config files
	* parse.pl.in: (gst_parse_slackware_hostname),
	  (gst_parse_rcinet1conf), (gst_parse_rcinet1conf_bool),
	  (gst_parse_wireless_opts): functions added to parse slackware network
	  config files

