	* general.pl.in (xst_directive_run): Wrong lowargs reporting. Better
	use scalar than $#.

	* file.pl.in (xst_file_run): was redirecting stderr to /dev/null twice.

	* replace.pl.in (xst_replace_split): minor indentation.

