	* xml.pl.in (xst_xml_scan_make_kid_array): Single quote (') can be used
	as an xml attribute enclosing symbol as well.

2001-12-20  Tambet Ingo  <tambet@ximian.com>

	* service.pl.in (xst_service_sysv_remove_link): Close dir also after
	opening it.
	(xst_service_sysv_set_links_active): Use stricter regexps to remove
	only service we need (xfs vs xfstt).
	(xst_service_sysv_set_links_inactive): Ditto.
	(xst_service_sysv_restart): Actually see what parameters got passed and
	use them. doh!

	* font.pl.in (xfs_reload): Use more compatible way to restart xfs.
	(x_font_set): Restart xfs only when needed.

